### Create paste (normal case)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/pastes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello World",
  "ttl_seconds": 60,
  "max_views": 2
}

### Fetch paste (replace <id> with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pastes/8e49d1fc-fa14-4753-9078-6a9ab4a3dae8

